# Weekly Scrum Report

Date: 2018-07-22

## Stand-up Questions

- What tasks did I work on / complete?
For the order management domain, completed following tasks-
1. Design REST API using RAML
2. Create a GetSandBox Mock Service
3. Design Data Model
4. Design database schema
5. Build REST service

- What am I planning to work on next?
1. Unit Testing
